{
  "3223370": {
    "name": "There's Nothing Underground",
    "steam_appid": 3223370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一款肉鸽解谜冒险游戏，在这款游戏里你需要用随机的工具以你能想象到的任何方式去通关。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每个关卡都可以有多种解法，每个工具和不同的关卡元素之间都可以彼此互动。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你肯定是跳不过去的，这下要怎么办？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/7b22c49fc044aab8ffda6bf53e1d5036.poster.avif?t=1765533222\" width=780 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/7b22c49fc044aab8ffda6bf53e1d5036.webm?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/7b22c49fc044aab8ffda6bf53e1d5036.mp4?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你有钩爪这事儿就好办了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/72b81854db35df93ff858d2d7b6960f2.poster.avif?t=1765533222\" width=780 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/72b81854db35df93ff858d2d7b6960f2.webm?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/72b81854db35df93ff858d2d7b6960f2.mp4?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者试试加速飞过去？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/70b699c0fb05b2451abf9f232e08bed2.poster.avif?t=1765533222\" width=780 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/70b699c0fb05b2451abf9f232e08bed2.webm?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/70b699c0fb05b2451abf9f232e08bed2.mp4?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >又或者直接把对面的平台拽过来然后跳上去？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/7896b288f2730efa54ea4d1c09323b40.poster.avif?t=1765533222\" width=780 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/7896b288f2730efa54ea4d1c09323b40.webm?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/7896b288f2730efa54ea4d1c09323b40.mp4?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直接用胶水和箱子搭一座桥也能行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/db3236ce2789cdce82b27acd906f93a6.poster.avif?t=1765533222\" width=780 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/db3236ce2789cdce82b27acd906f93a6.webm?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/db3236ce2789cdce82b27acd906f93a6.mp4?t=1765533222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次游戏中，你都能解锁、购买或发现新的工具！一切皆有可能，所以尽情发挥你的创意吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/b68dd5a26a89acded3efa616fd6b4179.avif?t=1765533222\" width=512 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20XX年，一颗巨大的小行星朝地球飞来——但它并未撞击，而是停在了地球上空。其核心深处蕴藏着的稀有材料引发了全球范围的采矿潮，至今已经持续了25年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演Gustav，一名经验丰富的工人，参与一项高风险任务：去调查一种从小行星深处传来的奇怪信号。然而，当你深入小行星的核心时，一切都开始变得不一样了。时间与空间的扭曲变形导致你跟你的队员失散，你无路可退，只能继续前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能到达核心并揭开小行星的秘密，还是会永远迷失在它的内部？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/9ce6f7688a04b6a3c72cdd9fa4c4643c.avif?t=1765533222\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras_big/9ce6f7688a04b6a3c72cdd9fa4c4643c.avif?t=1765533222 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223370/extras/e4ccd786cfefc093d58473052ad9bbb9.avif?t=1765533222\" width=512 height=128 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序化生成的地图：每次挑战都是独一无二的，因此需要你灵活地制定计划和策略。是走最短路线？还是花时间收集更强力的工具挑战高难关卡？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+种可以与场景互动的工具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >???+叙事片段</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
